  and <m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mi>T</m:mi></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>.
  
  As we determined from the analysis in the horizontal direction,
  
  
  <m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>T</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>L</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">=</m:mo><m:msub><m:mi>T</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>R</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">=</m:mo><m:mi>T</m:mi></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>:</para><para id="import-auto-id2126253"><equation id="eip-id3367015"><m:math>
            
