        </section><section id="fs-id1550370" type="problems-exercises" class="problems-exercises"><title>Problem Exercises</title><exercise id="fs-id2600233" type="problem-exercises"><problem id="fs-id2600234">
          <para id="import-auto-id1569366">Two teams of nine members each engage in a tug of war. Each of the first team’s members has an average mass of 68 kg and exerts an average force of 1350 N horizontally. Each of the second team’s members has an average mass of 73 kg and exerts an average force of 1365 N horizontally. (a) What is magnitude of the acceleration of the two teams? (b) What is the tension in the section of rope between the teams?</para></problem>
